{
  "stem": "13623.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And we're just-- they're just keeping us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "We're warehoused, so to speak, over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that point, I'm still with my father and with the same group.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're keeping-- we're all keeping together, the same group that we started out from our town, that we started out from the ghetto, some of the people that we made acquaintances in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're still the same group there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was nobody I can rely on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because even though I was with my father, which was nice, but there was nobody to rely on, because everybody was in the same boat.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody could help anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody can be of any assistance to anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was nice that I was with my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father's brother-in-law, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] his name-- we-- we called him [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wasn't a grandfather, but that was his nickname.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He had a brother and a sister that lived in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we were in Buchenwald, he got busy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We met people from different parts of the world there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were prisoners there from different parts, from different countries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wherever Germany came in, the Jews were deported.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he was busy looking for his brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He could-- he did not find him, but he got busy looking for him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "After being in Buchenwald for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what would be maybe a couple of weeks, they started to call names and numbers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they put-- they would be put on-- on trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And people-- every day, a group of people would leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't know where they-- where they went.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
